OL,5, More than 170 global figures have      
OL,6, called on Bangladesh's prime minister  
OL,7, Sheikh Hasina to stop the "persecution"
OL,8, of Nobel laureate Muhammad Yunus.      
OL,10,FProf Yunus - known internationally as  
OL,11,Fthe "banker to the poor" - has been    
OL,12,Fslapped with swathes of lawsuits, with 
OL,13,Fseveral more filed in recent weeks.    
OL,15,FThe open letter said these represented 
OL,16,Fan assault on democracy.               
OL,18,FMs Hasina responded harshly, accusing  
OL,19,Fthe 83-year-old of "begging" for an    
OL,20,Finternational statement.               
